EditorData.NodeContext: Starts out blissful, then actual recollection - vague puzzlement and horror

Text.Value: To see Her design... to see... HER...
You saw the Absolute? Tell me what She looked like.
Before the Absolute - who were you?
Elturgard... She spoke... in my dreams...
*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*
...I brought... converts... young souls... for the Absolute...
*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*
*The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*

Synopsis: The Speak With Dead dialog for the default fallback corpse that drops from the Cleansing Chute corpse. This corpse only appears when another minor character (presumably one of the tieflings) shouldn't end up dead here for some reason.
